data.description: Absolutely meticulous  3BR 3BA  rancher with a spacious 3300+ sq ft floorplan! With over 2300 sq ft on the main level, the 9ft ceilings, recessed lighting, lots of windows, nice neutral wall color, and more! The open kitchen has ample maple cabinetry and an island, light filled sunroom with vaulted ceilings overlooking backyard that faces the woods!  The family room had a convenient gas fireplace,  expansive primary suite with ample closet and spacious primary bath,  2 additional bedrooms, and 2nd full bath and laundry room round out the first floor.  Fully finished lower level has a 3rd full bath, expansive finished area perfect for a multitude of uses, storage room and walkout to back yard.  This property is complete with a 2 car garage, fenced rear yard and almost an acre of land.  The propane tank is off the driveway and is owned. Reasonable HOA fees, close to amenities and continuous up-to-date maintenance make this home a wise, move-in ready choice!
